---
title: Pork & Creamy Mushroom Sauce with Mash & Steamed Veggies
description: There's something magical about this mushroom sauce – it's loaded with umami, that savoury fifth taste, which makes it totally irresistible! Spoon it over tender pork steaks and add some fluffy mash for an unbelievably delicious dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-creamy-mushroom-sauce-fbb66b68.jpg
